\begin_layout Section
Before thinking about postdoc
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Published good and many papers.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Go to conference to make contact and find out what prof.
 are doing.
 Make list of people.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Make CV
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Make Web page
\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
During your last year
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Contact your listed people by saying thank you and wish them on their birth
 day or any specific occasional.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Learn writing email about introducing yourself.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Write research proposal include figure.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Make ppt in addition to research proposal.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Previous/Current Phd research
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
2/3 page what you are doing now
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Include attractive pictures.
 Graphical abstract will help here.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Highlight your skill relevant to publish papers.
 
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
Research proposal for postdoc position
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
What you will do in future related to post doc prof.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Define problem
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
How you will contribute to their lab.
\end_layout

\end_deeper
