\begin_layout Part
Academic position as faculty
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Become member of professional boards/institutions.
 It is good to take membership as it give wider connection for job and awards.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
Assistant Professor
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
Outline your most significant contribution towards research.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
How you as a faculty will contribute in the institute?
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
Present your vision for the department for the next five years.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
Outline your proposed road map for teaching and research for the next five
 years.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
How would you create an innovative learning environment?
\end_layout

